&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a platform-minded Product Manager to own the UI and user experience of Attain&#39;s Measurement platform—the product our agency, advertiser, and publisher clients use to connect media exposure directly to real sales outcomes. This is a dual-impact role: you&#39;ll drive internal efficiency for the teams who configure and manage measurement workflows, while building external-facing platform experiences that make it easier for clients to access, interpret, and act on their measurement results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll work at the intersection of data, design, and engineering to evolve the platform from setup through reporting—making in-flight measurement, incrementality, and attribution insights more accessible, actionable, and self-serve. This role reports directly to the Senior Director of Product, Measurement.&lt;/p&gt;
